# File     : GRND023-policy-issuance-policy.ttl
# Domain   : Deontic Ontology / ODRL Grounding
# Problem  : Policy issuance: Power to issue policy creates Subjection
# Refs     : Mohammed et al., What Does ODRL Mean? FOIS 2026
# Generated: 2026-03-18 by gen_foundation_problems.py
# Links    : Discriminating/GRND023-policy-issuance-1.p
#            Discriminating/GRND023-policy-issuance-1.smt2
